text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha chaur puok anak brab khnhom mk meul avei del a l laoh ban bratan dl puok anak nouv leaphosakkar haey puok anak ban thveu vea muoychamnuon tow chea robsa hamkhat ning chea robsa anounhnhat( tam tomneung chetd) . chaur anak pol tha tae a l laoh ban anounhnhat aoy puok anak ryy muoy puok anak bradit kohk champoh a l laoh
